---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import DimLine from '@/components/DimLine.astro';

const PRESS_CONTACT_EMAIL = 'reagan@start-suite.com';
const LAUNCH_DATE_DISPLAY = 'May 5, 2026';

const founders = [
  {
    name: 'Lucy Gonzalez',
    title: 'Co-Founder',
    photo: '/press/lucy-gonzalez-startsuite.jpg',
    alt: 'Lucy Gonzalez, Co-Founder of StartSuite',
    bio: [
      "Lucy Gonzalez is co-founder of StartSuite. She leads product, engineering, and the operational design of Brand HQ, the company's creative operating system.",
      "Before StartSuite, Lucy built creative infrastructure for early-stage operators across consumer, healthcare, and venture-backed software. Her work centers on the question of what protects judgment from getting watered down at scale, which is the question Brand HQ is built to answer.",
    ],
  },
  {
    name: 'Reagan Renfroe',
    title: 'Co-Founder',
    photo: '/press/reagan-renfroe-startsuite.jpg',
    alt: 'Reagan Renfroe, Co-Founder of StartSuite',
    bio: [
      "Reagan Renfroe is co-founder of StartSuite. He leads brand strategy, market positioning, and the editorial discipline that runs through every Brand HQ.",
      "Reagan has spent his career inside early-stage companies and the firms backing them, watching the same brand collapse pattern play out across categories. StartSuite is his answer to the question of what infrastructure makes that collapse not the default outcome.",
    ],
  },
];
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Press Kit — StartSuite"
  description="Press materials, founder bios, product facts, and downloadable brand assets for StartSuite. For media inquiries, contact Reagan Renfroe."
  ogTitle="StartSuite — Press Kit"
  ogDescription="A creative operating system for lean teams shipping at scale. Founder bios, product facts, and downloadable brand assets."
  noindex={true}
>
  <!-- ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
       HERO
       ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="pk-hero">
    <div class="pk-hero-inner">
      <div class="pill">Press Kit</div>
      <h1>
        StartSuite is a creative operating system for lean teams shipping at scale.
      </h1>
      <p class="pk-hero-lede">
        Other platforms in this category store context. Brand HQ makes it operational: humans curate the brand record, every AI tool plugged in inherits it, and the work ships at the speed of your leads.
      </p>
      <div class="pk-hero-meta">
        <div>
          <span class="pk-meta-label">Announced</span>
          <span class="pk-meta-value">{LAUNCH_DATE_DISPLAY}</span>
        </div>
        <div>
          <span class="pk-meta-label">Press contact</span>
          <a class="pk-meta-value pk-meta-link" href={`mailto:${PRESS_CONTACT_EMAIL}`}>{PRESS_CONTACT_EMAIL}</a>
        </div>
        <div>
          <a class="btn btn-primary" href="#assets">Download assets ↓</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <DimLine label="Why now" />

  <!-- ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
       WHY NOW (narrative)
       ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="pk-narrative">
    <div class="pk-narrative-inner">
      <div class="pk-narrative-eyebrow">Why now</div>
      <h2>The bottleneck in branding moved, and most companies haven't noticed.</h2>
      <div class="pk-narrative-body">
        <p>For two decades, the bottleneck was production. Hiring designers, briefing agencies, shipping content, getting the deck right before the meeting. Every brand stack built since the early 2000s was a different answer to the same problem, which was that producing on-brand work was slow and expensive.</p>
        <p>That constraint is gone. Any company with an AI tool can produce infinite on-brand-shaped output by Tuesday. The floor on creative work raised, the ceiling collapsed onto it, and the result is a market where every company is using the same tools to sound like the same company.</p>
        <p>The new bottleneck is curated context. Not "what can we make?" but "what's actually true about us, decided, current, and legible to both our team and the tools we're plugging in?" The companies that solve this get to build from a record that compounds. The companies that don't are renting their voice from whatever model they plugged in last quarter.</p>
        <p><strong>StartSuite is the bet that brand has become a context problem, not a content problem.</strong> Brand HQ is the curation layer where founder taste, market intelligence, and audience truth live as a working record. The outputs aren't files. They're companies that sound like themselves at scale.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
       PULL QUOTE BAND
       ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="pk-quote-band">
    <div class="pk-quote-inner">
      <span class="pk-quote-glyph" aria-hidden="true">"</span>
      <blockquote>
        As I was reading through, I was like, this is what I want. And I was like, wait, yeah, that's what we've always wanted for our other company.
      </blockquote>
      <figcaption>
        <span class="pk-quote-rule" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        Mike Lee, Co-Founder, Steadwell
      </figcaption>
    </div>
  </section>

  <DimLine label="Taste is the moat" />

  <!-- ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
       TASTE IS THE MOAT (narrative)
       ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="pk-narrative">
    <div class="pk-narrative-inner">
      <div class="pk-narrative-eyebrow">Taste is the moat</div>
      <h2>The defensible thing in branding has always been taste.</h2>
      <div class="pk-narrative-body">
        <p>The defensible thing in branding has always been taste — the founder's, the CMO's, the principal's, the operator who knows what's true about the company before anyone else does. Taste is the editorial judgment that distinguishes "this sounds right" from "this is a generic version of what an AI tool would write."</p>
        <p>For two decades, the constraint on taste was operational. The founder couldn't be in every meeting, couldn't review every brief, couldn't write every social post. So companies hired agencies, built creative ops teams, tried to systematize taste through brand guides nobody read. The compromise was always: real taste at the top, watered-down taste in production.</p>
        <p>The new tools collapsed both ends of that. The same AI that lets every contractor produce on-brand-shaped output also lets every founder push their actual judgment further into the system. The bottleneck moved from "can we produce more?" to "what's actually true about us, decided, current, and legible to both our team and the tools we're plugging in?"</p>
        <p><strong>That's what Brand HQ is.</strong> A curation layer. Founders, CMOs, and creative leads decide what gets to count as the company's voice. The system protects that record. Every AI tool plugged in inherits it. Every brief, every social signal, every draft sharpens what makes the company different instead of collapsing into the median voice every other company is also producing.</p>
        <p>The companies that figure this out first get to build from a record that compounds. The ones that don't are renting their voice from whatever model they plugged in last quarter.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <DimLine label="The product" />

  <!-- ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
       PRODUCT FAST FACTS
       ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="pk-facts section-alt">
    <div class="pk-facts-inner">
      <div class="pk-facts-eyebrow">Product fast facts</div>
      <h2>What Brand HQ does, in one screen.</h2>
      <ul class="pk-facts-list">
        <li><strong>A working brand record, not a brand guide.</strong> Curation is the product.</li>
        <li><strong>Five sections per company.</strong> Brand DNA, Verbal Identity, Visual Identity, Audience, Market Intelligence.</li>
        <li><strong>Designed for the human-in-the-loop.</strong> Captured signals — meetings, agents, mentions — enter pending review. Humans decide what becomes canonical.</li>
        <li><strong>Tier-of-authority architecture.</strong> Distinguishes captured-but-not-decided from canonical. AI tools query the canonical layer; the captured layer remains visible for context without polluting the official record.</li>
        <li><strong>Built for AI-native workflows.</strong> Every brief, every prompt, every plug-in inherits the curated record.</li>
        <li><strong>Multi-client by design.</strong> Operators running portfolios get a workspace per company plus a portfolio command center.</li>
        <li><strong>Real-time market intelligence layer.</strong> Connects competitor moves and audience signals to the company's own positioning.</li>
        <li><strong>Living, not static.</strong> Every Brand HQ updates as the company evolves; the record never goes stale.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
       QUICK FACTS
       ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="pk-quick">
    <div class="pk-quick-inner">
      <div class="pk-quick-eyebrow">Quick facts</div>
      <dl class="pk-quick-grid">
        <div class="pk-quick-row">
          <dt>Founded</dt>
          <dd>2026</dd>
        </div>
        <div class="pk-quick-row">
          <dt>Founders</dt>
          <dd>Lucy Gonzalez and Reagan Renfroe</dd>
        </div>
        <div class="pk-quick-row">
          <dt>Headquarters</dt>
          <dd>Nashville and Tulsa</dd>
        </div>
        <div class="pk-quick-row">
          <dt>Public launch</dt>
          <dd>{LAUNCH_DATE_DISPLAY}</dd>
        </div>
        <div class="pk-quick-row">
          <dt>Powered by</dt>
          <dd>46</dd>
        </div>
        <div class="pk-quick-row">
          <dt>Early customers</dt>
          <dd>Companies across venture capital, sports media, wellness, and industrial operations</dd>
        </div>
        <div class="pk-quick-row">
          <dt>Product</dt>
          <dd>Brand HQ, a creative operating system for lean teams shipping at scale</dd>
        </div>
      </dl>
    </div>
  </section>

  <DimLine label="Founders" />

  <!-- ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
       FOUNDERS
       ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="pk-founders">
    <div class="pk-founders-inner">
      {founders.map((founder) => (
        <div class="pk-founder">
          <div class="pk-founder-photo">
            <img src={founder.photo} alt={founder.alt} loading="lazy" />
          </div>
          <div class="pk-founder-body">
            <h3>{founder.name}</h3>
            <p class="pk-founder-title">{founder.title}</p>
            {founder.bio.map((paragraph) => (
              <p>{paragraph}</p>
            ))}
            <a class="pk-founder-download" href={founder.photo} download>
              Download headshot ↓
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>
  </section>

  <DimLine label="Assets" />

  <!-- ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
       ASSETS — downloadable
       ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="pk-assets section-alt" id="assets">
    <div class="pk-assets-inner">
      <div class="pk-assets-eyebrow">Downloads</div>
      <h2>Brand assets, headshots, and screenshots.</h2>
      <p class="pk-assets-note">All files downloadable directly. No email gate.</p>

      <div class="pk-asset-grid">
        <!-- Logo pack -->
        <div class="pk-asset-card">
          <div class="pk-asset-head">
            <span class="pk-asset-tag">Logos</span>
            <h3>Logo pack</h3>
            <p>Full mark and mark-only, light and dark backgrounds, SVG and PNG. 8 files.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="pk-asset-actions">
            <a class="btn btn-outline" href="/press/startsuite-logos.zip" download>Download .zip ↓</a>
            <ul class="pk-asset-files">
              <li><a href="/press/logos/startsuite-mark-full-light.svg" download>Full mark · light · SVG</a></li>
              <li><a href="/press/logos/startsuite-mark-full-light.png" download>Full mark · light · PNG</a></li>
              <li><a href="/press/logos/startsuite-mark-full-dark.svg" download>Full mark · dark · SVG</a></li>
              <li><a href="/press/logos/startsuite-mark-full-dark.png" download>Full mark · dark · PNG</a></li>
              <li><a href="/press/logos/startsuite-mark-only-light.svg" download>Mark only · light · SVG</a></li>
              <li><a href="/press/logos/startsuite-mark-only-light.png" download>Mark only · light · PNG</a></li>
              <li><a href="/press/logos/startsuite-mark-only-dark.svg" download>Mark only · dark · SVG</a></li>
              <li><a href="/press/logos/startsuite-mark-only-dark.png" download>Mark only · dark · PNG</a></li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Headshots -->
        <div class="pk-asset-card">
          <div class="pk-asset-head">
            <span class="pk-asset-tag">Headshots</span>
            <h3>Founder headshots</h3>
            <p>2000px+ wide. Color, hi-res, print-ready.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="pk-asset-actions">
            <ul class="pk-asset-files">
              <li><a href="/press/lucy-gonzalez-startsuite.jpg" download>Lucy Gonzalez · JPG</a></li>
              <li><a href="/press/reagan-renfroe-startsuite.jpg" download>Reagan Renfroe · JPG</a></li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Product screenshots -->
        <div class="pk-asset-card">
          <div class="pk-asset-head">
            <span class="pk-asset-tag">Product</span>
            <h3>Product screenshots</h3>
            <p>3–5 captioned screenshots. Lead with Brand HQ navigation.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="pk-asset-actions">
            <a class="btn btn-outline" href="/press/startsuite-product-screenshots.zip" download>Download .zip ↓</a>
            <ul class="pk-asset-files pk-placeholder">
              <li><em>[Screenshot list — Lucy/Reagan to confirm captions and order]</em></li>
              <li><a href="/press/screenshots/brand-hq-navigation.png" download>Brand HQ navigation · PNG</a></li>
              <li><a href="/press/screenshots/brand-hq-record.png" download>Brand HQ record · PNG</a></li>
              <li><a href="/press/screenshots/brand-hq-signal.png" download>Brand HQ signal · PNG</a></li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Brand Guide — live preview, internal link -->
        <a class="pk-asset-card pk-asset-card-link pk-brand-guide" href="/brand-guide">
          <div class="pk-asset-head">
            <span class="pk-asset-tag">Brand Guide</span>
            <h3>StartSuite Brand Guide</h3>
            <p>A live preview, not a static PDF. Color, typography, voice, and the decisions behind them — current as of today, updated as the brand evolves.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="pk-asset-actions">
            <div class="pk-swatches" aria-hidden="true">
              <span class="pk-swatch-chip pk-swatch-chip-sm" style="background:#7B2FBE"></span>
              <span class="pk-swatch-chip pk-swatch-chip-sm" style="background:#F3EAFC;border:1px solid var(--border-hi)"></span>
              <span class="pk-swatch-chip pk-swatch-chip-sm" style="background:#1A1A2E"></span>
            </div>
            <span class="pk-brand-guide-cta">View Brand Guide →</span>
          </div>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <DimLine label="Press contact" />

  <!-- ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
       PRESS CONTACT
       ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="pk-contact">
    <div class="pk-contact-inner">
      <div class="pk-contact-eyebrow">Press contact</div>
      <p class="pk-contact-name">Reagan Renfroe</p>
      <a class="pk-contact-email" href={`mailto:${PRESS_CONTACT_EMAIL}`}>{PRESS_CONTACT_EMAIL}</a>
      <p class="pk-contact-sla">Responses within 4 business hours during launch week, 1 business day after.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
       BOILERPLATE
       ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="pk-boilerplate">
    <div class="pk-boilerplate-inner">
      <div class="pk-boilerplate-eyebrow">Boilerplate</div>
      <p>
        StartSuite is a creative operating system for lean teams shipping at scale. Its product, Brand HQ, is a curated record of how a company sounds, decides, and shows up, built so every creative brief, social signal, and AI-generated draft sharpens what makes you different instead of collapsing into the median voice AI tools default to. Founded in 2026 by Lucy Gonzalez and Reagan Renfroe and powered by 46, StartSuite serves early customers across venture capital, sports media, wellness, and industrial operations. The company launched publicly on {LAUNCH_DATE_DISPLAY}.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
       Structured data — Organization
       ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify({
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "Organization",
    "name": "StartSuite",
    "url": "https://start-suite.com",
    "logo": "https://start-suite.com/images/logo-full-dark.png",
    "foundingDate": "2026",
    "founders": [
      { "@type": "Person", "name": "Lucy Gonzalez" },
      { "@type": "Person", "name": "Reagan Renfroe" }
    ],
    "description": "A creative operating system for lean teams shipping at scale.",
    "contactPoint": {
      "@type": "ContactPoint",
      "contactType": "press",
      "email": PRESS_CONTACT_EMAIL,
      "name": "Reagan Renfroe"
    }
  })} />
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  /* ─── HERO ─────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
  .pk-hero{
    padding:160px 48px 80px;
    position:relative;overflow:hidden;
  }
  .pk-hero::before{
    content:'';position:absolute;top:-200px;left:30%;
    width:900px;height:600px;pointer-events:none;
    background:radial-gradient(ellipse,rgba(139,109,181,0.08) 0%,transparent 60%);
  }
  .pk-hero-inner{
    max-width:980px;margin:0 auto;position:relative;z-index:1;
  }
  .pk-hero h1{
    font-size:clamp(36px,4.6vw,58px);
    background:linear-gradient(160deg,#fff 30%,var(--accent) 100%);
    -webkit-background-clip:text;-webkit-text-fill-color:transparent;
    background-clip:text;
    letter-spacing:-0.035em;line-height:1.08;
    margin-bottom:28px;
  }
  .pk-hero-lede{
    font-size:18px;line-height:1.7;
    color:var(--text-muted);
    max-width:760px;margin-bottom:48px;
  }
  .pk-hero-meta{
    display:flex;align-items:flex-end;gap:48px;flex-wrap:wrap;
    padding-top:32px;border-top:1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .pk-hero-meta > div{
    display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:4px;
  }
  .pk-meta-label{
    font-family:var(--mono);
    font-size:10px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:0.16em;
    text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--text-dim);
  }
  .pk-meta-value{
    font-size:15px;font-weight:600;color:var(--text);
    letter-spacing:-0.01em;
  }
  .pk-meta-link{
    color:var(--purple-light);text-decoration:none;
    transition:color var(--duration) var(--ease);
  }
  .pk-meta-link:hover{color:var(--text)}

  /* ─── NARRATIVE ────────────────────────────────────────────── */
  .pk-narrative{
    padding:80px 48px;
  }
  .pk-narrative-inner{
    max-width:780px;margin:0 auto;
  }
  .pk-narrative-eyebrow{
    font-family:var(--mono);
    font-size:10px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:0.18em;
    text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--purple-light);
    margin-bottom:20px;
  }
  .pk-narrative h2{
    font-size:clamp(28px,3.6vw,42px);
    letter-spacing:-0.03em;line-height:1.15;
    color:var(--text);
    margin-bottom:36px;
  }
  .pk-narrative-body p{
    font-size:16px;line-height:1.85;
    color:var(--text-muted);
    margin-bottom:20px;
  }
  .pk-narrative-body p:last-child{margin-bottom:0}
  .pk-narrative-body strong{color:var(--text);font-weight:600}

  /* ─── PULL QUOTE BAND ──────────────────────────────────────── */
  .pk-quote-band{
    padding:96px 48px;
    background:
      radial-gradient(ellipse 700px 380px at 50% 50%,rgba(196,169,224,0.13) 0%,transparent 65%),
      linear-gradient(160deg,rgba(139,109,181,0.13) 0%,rgba(91,70,135,0.07) 50%,rgba(58,42,90,0.05) 100%);
    border-top:1px solid rgba(139,109,181,0.22);
    border-bottom:1px solid rgba(139,109,181,0.22);
    position:relative;overflow:hidden;
  }
  .pk-quote-band::before{
    content:'';position:absolute;top:0;left:0;right:0;height:1px;
    background:linear-gradient(90deg,transparent,rgba(196,169,224,0.5),transparent);
  }
  .pk-quote-inner{
    max-width:880px;margin:0 auto;
    display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;
    text-align:center;gap:28px;
  }
  .pk-quote-glyph{
    font-family:'Georgia','Times New Roman',serif;
    font-size:clamp(80px,9vw,140px);
    line-height:0.4;
    color:var(--purple-light);
    opacity:0.32;
    font-style:italic;letter-spacing:-0.05em;
  }
  .pk-quote-band blockquote{
    font-family:'Georgia','Times New Roman',serif;
    font-size:clamp(22px,2.8vw,34px);
    line-height:1.36;letter-spacing:-0.02em;
    color:var(--text);
    font-style:italic;font-weight:400;
    margin:0;max-width:760px;
  }
  .pk-quote-band figcaption{
    font-family:var(--mono);
    font-size:11px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:0.16em;
    text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--purple-light);
    display:flex;align-items:center;gap:14px;
  }
  .pk-quote-rule{
    display:inline-block;width:36px;height:1px;
    background:var(--purple-light);opacity:0.5;
  }

  /* ─── PRODUCT FAST FACTS ───────────────────────────────────── */
  .pk-facts{
    padding:100px 48px;
  }
  .pk-facts-inner{
    max-width:980px;margin:0 auto;
  }
  .pk-facts-eyebrow{
    font-family:var(--mono);
    font-size:10px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:0.18em;
    text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--purple-light);
    margin-bottom:20px;
  }
  .pk-facts h2{
    font-size:clamp(28px,3.6vw,42px);
    letter-spacing:-0.03em;line-height:1.15;
    margin-bottom:40px;
  }
  .pk-facts-list{
    list-style:none;padding:0;margin:0;
    display:flex;flex-direction:column;
    border-top:1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .pk-facts-list li{
    padding:22px 0;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);
    font-size:15px;line-height:1.7;color:var(--text-muted);
  }
  .pk-facts-list li strong{
    color:var(--text);font-weight:700;
    margin-right:6px;
  }

  /* ─── QUICK FACTS ──────────────────────────────────────────── */
  .pk-quick{
    padding:100px 48px;
  }
  .pk-quick-inner{
    max-width:980px;margin:0 auto;
  }
  .pk-quick-eyebrow{
    font-family:var(--mono);
    font-size:10px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:0.18em;
    text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--purple-light);
    margin-bottom:28px;
  }
  .pk-quick-grid{
    margin:0;border-top:1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .pk-quick-row{
    display:grid;grid-template-columns:220px 1fr;gap:24px;
    padding:18px 0;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);
    align-items:baseline;
  }
  .pk-quick-row dt{
    font-family:var(--mono);
    font-size:11px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:0.14em;
    text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--text-dim);
    margin:0;
  }
  .pk-quick-row dd{
    font-size:15px;line-height:1.7;color:var(--text);
    margin:0;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:-0.005em;
  }

  /* ─── FOUNDERS ─────────────────────────────────────────────── */
  .pk-founders{
    padding:80px 48px 100px;
  }
  .pk-founders-inner{
    max-width:1100px;margin:0 auto;
